## Additional Acknowledgments

This software incorporates educational standards and guidelines from:

- Uganda National Examinations Board (UNEB)
- National Curriculum Development Centre (NCDC)
- Ministry of Education and Sports, Uganda

The implementation of Uganda's educational curriculum and grading systems in this
software is based on publicly available educational standards and is intended
to support educational institutions in Uganda.

